Files for making stuff work right in XBMC

 - keyboard_addon_bindings.xml
    - Maps XBMC keys to addon actions
    - Add a symlink to this file from within XBMC's userdata/keymaps directory

 - script.avr-control-client
    - Addon for forwarding XBMC events to an external AVR Controller
    - Add a symlink to this directory from within XBMC's addon directory
